        <headline>Heat Advisory issued August 8 at 11:47AM MDT until August 8 at 7:00PM MDT by NWS Albuquerque NM</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...Temperatures near 105 degrees in Chaves County including
Roswell.

* WHERE...Chaves County Plains.

* WHEN...Until 7 PM MDT this evening.

* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures may cause heat illnesses.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
